{"tid":1597520,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「突發」英國外相促中方遵守《中英聯合聲明》  (9/27/10:11)","createTime":"2019-09-27T03:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T11:37:45.000Z","uid":30788,"like":108,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":81,"replies":[{"pid":"5f9ecc2a7e7d33945824fdd639ad4b901e58b4e8","tid":1597520,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:37:59.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】英國外相藍韜文重申《中英聯合聲明》仍然有效，英國會繼續支持「一國兩制」，同時關注香港人權狀況。 <br />\n<br />\n藍韜文在國會下議院就香港問題接受議員緊急質詢。他表示，曾經向北京及香港特區政府表明英國會繼續支持「一國兩制」，強調《中英聯合聲明》至今仍然有效，促請中方遵守。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，英國政府關注人權，特別是行使權利，他譴責部分暴力行為，但強調進行和平及合法集會的市民不應受到不合適對待。"},{"pid":"35b47aaa0eb28be33bb0890f85d453a2df0975a7","tid":1597520,"uid":65790,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:38:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港自治</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2fa246360eca85aba3b545be1763d71a1270360b","tid":1597520,"uid":68689,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"唔平權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e166b866c119ce2a391404e17bf8ae2917aee9","tid":1597520,"uid":191762,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2fa246360eca85aba3b545be1763d71a1270360b","tid":1597520,"uid":68689,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"唔平權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"救港先啦"},{"pid":"35d74507eb970021d8a0bb2cf5331a88afe4f1a6","tid":1597520,"uid":244809,"like":19,"dislike":5,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:39:58.000Z","msg":"收皮，英國佬<br />\n你搞掂自己擅野先<br />\n一開始又係你出賣港人先"},{"pid":"1d2be0e1814da163ea9e3b7a8b17abf430e8bc7a","tid":1597520,"uid":290118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T03:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又口交"},{"pid":"d61666b7668